name: 名字
extraProbability: 自动钓鱼额外成功率（同类增益互相相加）
extraSpeed: 使用时提升进度上升速度
lowerSpeed: 使用时降低进度下降速度

name: Starter fishing rod
_desc: Bare branches, good toughness, barely a fishing rod
_desc_tw: 光禿禿的樹枝，韌性不錯，勉強算是個魚竿吧
_desc_en: Bare branches, good toughness, barely a fishing rod
_desc_kr: 민둥민둥한 나뭇가지, 꽤 단단해 낚싯대로 사용할 수 있을 것 같다.

name: Junior fishing rod
_desc: Simply made of polished branch, seems to be slightly better
_desc_tw: 拋光樹枝後簡單制作的釣竿，性能似乎要稍微好點
_desc_en: Simply made of polished branch, seems to be slightly better
_desc_kr: 나뭇가지로 간단히 만든 낚싯대, 성능이 조금 나아진 것 같다.

name: Veteran fishing rod
_desc: The fishing rod made of reinforced plastic has good strength and performance
_desc_tw: 強化塑料制成的釣竿，擁有不錯的強度和性能
_desc_en: The fishing rod made of reinforced plastic has good strength and performance
_desc_kr: 강화 재료로 만든 낚싯대, 나쁘지 않은 성능을 보여준다.

name: Advanced fishing rod
_desc: The fishing rod made of metal has excellent strength and performance
_desc_tw: 金屬制成的魚竿，強度和性能都非常優秀
_desc_en: The fishing rod made of metal has excellent strength and performance
_desc_kr: 금속 재질의 낚싯대, 강도와 성능이 매우 우수하다.

name: Premium fishing rod
_desc: Specially made fishing rod made of carbon fiber, with excellent performance
_desc_tw: 碳化纖維特殊制作的魚竿，擁有極好的性能
_desc_en: Specially made fishing rod made of carbon fiber, with excellent performance
_desc_kr: 탄소섬유로 특수 제작된 낚싯대, 매우 뛰어난 성능을 지니고 있다.

name: Swift Fishing Rod
_desc: Specially made fishing rod made of carbon fiber, improved in some functions
_desc_tw: 碳化纖維特殊制作的魚竿，在某些功能上進行了神秘改良
_desc_en: Specially made fishing rod made of carbon fiber, improved in some functions
_desc_kr: 탄소섬유로 특수 제작된 낚싯대, 특정 기능을 개조했다.
